  "text": "Deterministic algorithm has high requirement in memory and CPU time, so it is often used to solve small-scale UA-FLP and reference [CITATION_1] proved its effectiveness. Heuristic algorithm and intelligent algorithms have faster calculation speed and are suitable for large-scale UA-FLP. Furthermore, genetic algorithm is most widely used, and different genetic algorithms were developed for various UA-FLPs.",
