  "bib_entries": {
    "111493910": {
      "title": "Modeling and solution algorithms for facility layout of manufacturing systems",
      "abstract": "To improve enterprises' market-response ability and competitiveness,facility layout in manufacturing system design was proposed.Correlated concepts and layout forms under different classification criteria were introduced.The application extents and advantages/disadvantages of diversified facility layout were presented.Optimization objectives and constraint conditions of facility layout were summarized.The modeling technologies and models of facility layout were gathered up.Furthermore,solution algorithms to solve the models were summed up.Finally,some research gaps in the existing research were discussed,which could provide reference for facility layout design and reconfiguration in the future."
    }
  },
